story.text: He was dissapointing. Reflecting whether the hereditary life is good or bad for society. Buffett hates it. I don't benefit from it. Leads to inbreeding. Why was I so insistent to come visit these hereditary aristocracy? Its quite dumb isn't it?
Scotland is so rural and lovely. A range between relaxing and boring.
